  "description": "<p>📍 Location: Changi South</p><p>📄 Employment Type: 1-Year Renewable Contract <br /></p><p>⏰ Working Shifts & Allowances</p><p>Morning Shift: 8:00 AM – 5:45 PM <br /></p><p>Afternoon Shift: 1:45 PM – 11:30 PM </p><p>▸ Shift allowance $10 per shift/day<br /></p><p>Night Shift: 11:00 PM – 8:45 AM </p><p>▸ Shift allowance $15 per shift/day<br /></p><p>🗓 Work Schedule:</p><p>Candidates must be open to working Mon–Fri OR Thurs–Mon</p><p><br />💰 Salary</p><p>Up to $2,800, depending on experience and shift assigned</p><p><br />🚌 Company Transport Provided</p><p>Pick-up points available at:</p><p>- Sengkang</p><p>- Ang Mo Kio</p><p>- Woodlands</p><p>- Pasir Ris</p><p><br />🔧 Job Scope</p><p>- Picking, packing, sorting, and labelling of industrial servers and equipment (large & heavy items) — not office-use servers.</p><p>- Loading and unloading of goods using handling equipment up to 20kg</p><p>- Assisting with warehouse operations and inventory movement</p><p>- Operating material handling machines (training provided)</p><p>- Ensuring safe handling of heavy items and compliance with safety procedures</p><p><br />📩 WHATSAPP wa.me/6589387313 TO APPLY🎊</p><p>Code: <strong>WAREEAST</strong></p><p>Full name:</p><p>Residential area:</p><p>Earliest availability date:</p><p>Commitment period:</p><p>Able to work on weekends?:</p><p>And please attached a copy of your resume</p><p><br />https://t.me/sgbesttempjobs</p><p>https://t.me/varioustempjobs</p><p><br />Chia Xin Ee Crystal | R21103390</p><p>EA License No: 21C0626</p>",
